{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Design a world-class luxury eCommerce hero section for Universes RAW, a premium men's fashion brand. The design must feel as polished and premium as luxury brands like Tom Ford, ZEGNA, Ralph Lauren Purple Label, or Brunello Cucinelli, while maintaining a modern, conversion-focused shopping experience.
    
    Overall Style
    Minimal, luxurious, premium editorial aesthetic
    Matte black, charcoal, dark gray, and subtle gold accents
    Cinematic studio lighting with soft shadows
    Clean premium typography with generous spacing
    Ultra-modern UI with elegant micro-interactions
    High-end fashion campaign look
    Fast loading and optimized for Shopify
    Hero Layout
    Full-width responsive hero section
    Viewport height: 90–100vh on desktop
    Mobile optimized without cropping important content
    Large empty space for promotional text and CTA
    Perfect visual balance between content and image
    Premium fade overlays for readability
    Background
    
    Use a luxurious fashion campaign image featuring:
    
    Premium male model
    Luxury fashion studio
    Dark premium interior
    Soft spotlight lighting
    Cinematic atmosphere
    Luxury clothing and accessories
    Matte textures
    Premium depth of field
    High-end editorial photography
    Ultra realistic
    No text inside the image
    Left Content
    
    Large premium heading
    
    Example:
    PREMIUM MEN'S FASHION
    
    Supporting text:
    Imported Fashion.
    Luxury Quality.
    Exclusive Collection.
    
    Primary CTA
    • Shop Now
    
    Secondary CTA
    • New Arrivals
    
    Buttons should have elegant hover animations, rounded corners, premium shadows, and subtle gold accents.
    
    Right Side
    
    Large premium fashion lifestyle image with:
    
    Luxury male model
    Elegant pose
    Premium styling
    Rich lighting
    Realistic skin tones
    High-end fashion photography
    Trust Bar
    
    Directly below the hero:
    
    Express Delivery
    Cash on Delivery
    Easy Exchange
    Premium Quality
    
    Use premium outlined icons with subtle gold highlights.
    
    Navigation
    
    Transparent glass navigation that becomes solid while scrolling.
    
    Include:
    
    Logo
    Home
    Shop
    Collections
    New Arrivals
    Store Locator
    Search
    Wishlist
    Account
    Cart
    
    Desktop:
    Centered navigation with spacious layout.
    
    Mobile:
    
    Hamburger menu
    Slide-out premium drawer
    Sticky header
    Large touch-friendly icons
    Responsive Design
    Desktop (1920px+)
    Large cinematic hero
    Text on left
    Model on right
    Plenty of whitespace
    Elegant transitions
    Laptop (1440px)
    
    Maintain perfect proportions.
    
    Tablet
    
    Scale typography and image while keeping CTAs visible.
    
    Mobile (375–430px)
    Stack content vertically
    Hero image remains premium and visible
    Heading scales perfectly
    CTA buttons full-width
    Thumb-friendly spacing
    No horizontal scrolling
    Optimized for one-handed use
    Animations
    Smooth fade-in
    Image parallax (subtle)
    Button hover glow
    Premium page transitions
    Soft floating effects
    Scroll reveal animations
    Luxury loading animation
    UI Design
    24px border radius
    Frosted glass elements
    Soft shadows
    Premium gradients
    Elegant dividers
    Minimal visual noise
    Consistent spacing using an 8-point grid
    Performance
    Optimized for Core Web Vitals
    Lazy-loaded hero image
    Responsive image sizes
    Fast mobile rendering
    SEO friendly
    Accessibility compliant
    Brand Feeling
    
    The final design should instantly communicate:
    
    Luxury
    Premium quality
    Confidence
    Exclusivity
    Modern fashion
    High trust
    High conversion
    International brand identity
    
    The hero section should look like a premium fashion campaign while remaining clean, elegant, responsive, and optimized for both desktop and mobile shopping experiences.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: {{ block.settings.hero_height_desktop }}vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__background {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__background img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__background-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2d2d2d 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__background-placeholder svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
    max-height: 600px;
    opacity: 0.1;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      {{ block.settings.overlay_color }} 0%,
      {{ block.settings.overlay_color | color_modify: 'alpha', 0.7 }} 50%,
      {{ block.settings.overlay_color | color_modify: 'alpha', 0 }} 100%
    );
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.container_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 {{ block.settings.container_padding }}px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: {{ block.settings.content_spacing }}px;
    animation: luxury-hero-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} 1s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes luxury-hero-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__eyebrow {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_size }}px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_spacing }}px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_color }};
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__heading {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.heading_weight }};
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.heading_spacing }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.heading_transform }};
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__subheading {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_size }}px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.6;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subheading_color }};
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.buttons_margin_top }}px;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: {{ block.settings.button_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.button_padding_horizontal }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.button_font_weight }};
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: {{ block.settings.button_border_width }}px solid;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__button--primary {
    background: {{ block.settings.primary_button_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.primary_button_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.primary_button_border }};
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px {{ block.settings.primary_button_bg | color_modify: 'alpha', 0.3 }};
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__button--primary:hover {
    background: {{ block.settings.primary_button_hover_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.primary_button_hover_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.primary_button_hover_border }};
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px {{ block.settings.primary_button_hover_bg | color_modify: 'alpha', 0.4 }};
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__button--secondary {
    background: {{ block.settings.secondary_button_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.secondary_button_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.secondary_button_border }};
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__button--secondary:hover {
    background: {{ block.settings.secondary_button_hover_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.secondary_button_hover_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.secondary_button_hover_border }};
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    animation: luxury-hero-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} 1.2s ease-out 0.3s both;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.image_border_radius }}px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a2a2a 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.image_border_radius }}px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__image-placeholder svg {
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
    opacity: 0.15;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__empty-state {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 30px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    text-align: center;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-bar {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
    width: 100%;
    background: {{ block.settings.trust_bar_bg }};
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border-top: 1px solid {{ block.settings.trust_bar_border }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.trust_bar_padding }}px 0;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-container {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.container_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 {{ block.settings.container_padding }}px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-icon {
    width: {{ block.settings.trust_icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.trust_icon_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.trust_icon_color }};
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-text {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.trust_text_size }}px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: {{ block.settings.trust_text_color }};
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__container {
      gap: 60px;
    }

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__heading {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.heading_size }}px * 0.7);
    }

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-container {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 30px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      min-height: {{ block.settings.hero_height_mobile }}vh;
    }

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__overlay {
      background: linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        {{ block.settings.overlay_color }} 0%,
        {{ block.settings.overlay_color | color_modify: 'alpha', 0.8 }} 50%,
        {{ block.settings.overlay_color | color_modify: 'alpha', 0.3 }} 100%
      );
    }

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      padding: 60px {{ block.settings.container_padding }}px;
    }

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__content {
      gap: {{ block.settings.content_spacing_mobile }}px;
      text-align: {{ block.settings.mobile_text_align }};
    }

    {% if block.settings.mobile_text_align == 'center' %}
      .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__content {
        align-items: center;
      }
    {% else %}
      .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__content {
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
    {% endif %}

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__eyebrow {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.eyebrow_size }}px * 0.85);
    }

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__heading {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size_mobile }}px;
    }

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__subheading {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.subheading_size }}px * 0.9);
    }

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: {{ block.settings.buttons_margin_top_mobile }}px;
    }

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: {{ block.settings.button_padding_vertical_mobile }}px {{ block.settings.button_padding_horizontal_mobile }}px;
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.button_font_size }}px * 0.9);
    }

    {% if block.settings.mobile_image_position == 'top' %}
      .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__image-wrapper {
        order: -1;
      }
    {% else %}
      .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__image-wrapper {
        order: 1;
      }
    {% endif %}

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-item {
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-icon {
      width: calc({{ block.settings.trust_icon_size }}px * 0.85);
      height: calc({{ block.settings.trust_icon_size }}px * 0.85);
    }

    .luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-text {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.trust_text_size }}px * 0.9);
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__background">
    {% if block.settings.background_image %}
      <img
        src="{{ block.settings.background_image | image_url: width: 2400 }}"
        srcset="{{ block.settings.background_image | image_url: width: 750 }} 750w,
                {{ block.settings.background_image | image_url: width: 1500 }} 1500w,
                {{ block.settings.background_image | image_url: width: 2400 }} 2400w"
        sizes="100vw"
        alt="{{ block.settings.background_image.alt | escape }}"
        loading="eager"
        width="{{ block.settings.background_image.width }}"
        height="{{ block.settings.background_image.height }}"
      >
    {% else %}
      <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__background-placeholder">
        {{ 'hero-apparel-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__overlay"></div>

  <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__container">
    <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__content">
      {% if block.settings.eyebrow != blank %}
        <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__eyebrow">
          {{ block.settings.eyebrow }}
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
        <h1 class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__heading">
          {{ block.settings.heading }}
        </h1>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.subheading != blank %}
        <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__subheading">
          {{ block.settings.subheading }}
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__buttons">
        {% if block.settings.primary_button_label != blank %}
          <a
            href="{{ block.settings.primary_button_link }}"
            class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__button luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__button--primary"
          >
            {{ block.settings.primary_button_label }}
          </a>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.secondary_button_label != blank %}
          <a
            href="{{ block.settings.secondary_button_link }}"
            class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__button luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__button--secondary"
          >
            {{ block.settings.secondary_button_label }}
          </a>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__image-wrapper">
      {% if block.settings.featured_image %}
        <img
          src="{{ block.settings.featured_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
          srcset="{{ block.settings.featured_image | image_url: width: 400 }} 400w,
                  {{ block.settings.featured_image | image_url: width: 600 }} 600w,
                  {{ block.settings.featured_image | image_url: width: 800 }} 800w"
          sizes="(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 50vw"
          alt="{{ block.settings.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
          loading="eager"
          width="{{ block.settings.featured_image.width }}"
          height="{{ block.settings.featured_image.height }}"
          class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__image"
        >
      {% else %}
        <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__image-placeholder">
          {{ 'product-apparel-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
          <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__empty-state">
            Add a premium model image
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>

  {% if block.settings.show_trust_bar %}
    <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-bar">
      <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-container">
        {% if block.settings.trust_item_1 != blank %}
          <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-item">
            <svg class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-text">{{ block.settings.trust_item_1 }}</span>
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.trust_item_2 != blank %}
          <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-item">
            <svg class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-text">{{ block.settings.trust_item_2 }}</span>
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.trust_item_3 != blank %}
          <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-item">
            <svg class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-text">{{ block.settings.trust_item_3 }}</span>
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.trust_item_4 != blank %}
          <div class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-item">
            <svg class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
              <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__trust-text">{{ block.settings.trust_item_4 }}</span>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endif %}
</luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class LuxuryHero{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.initParallax();
      }

      initParallax() {
        const background = this.querySelector('.luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}__background img');
        if (!background) return;

        let ticking = false;

        const updateParallax = () => {
          const scrolled = window.pageYOffset;
          const rate = scrolled * 0.3;
          background.style.transform = `translateY(${rate}px)`;
          ticking = false;
        };

        const requestTick = () => {
          if (!ticking) {
            window.requestAnimationFrame(updateParallax);
            ticking = true;
          }
        };

        window.addEventListener('scroll', requestTick, { passive: true });
      }
    }

    customElements.define('luxury-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}', LuxuryHero{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
